System::Boolean PropertyValueCollection::Contains (  NAMESPACE_OSGEO_FDO_COMMANDS::PropertyValue *  value  ) 
 

Determines whether the collection contains a specific NAMESPACE_OSGEO_FDO_COMMANDS::PropertyValue object.

Parameters:
value Input The NAMESPACE_OSGEO_FDO_COMMANDS::PropertyValue object to search in the collection.
Returns:
Returns true if the value is found in the collection; otherwise, false.
